The '''Illustrious Chieftain of Junkyards''' was the leader of the [[Squib Merchandising Consortium]] and thus of the entire [[Squib/Legends|Squib]] species. In the final days of the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Old Republic]] and the early years of the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]], [[Ebareebaveebeedee]] held the post. The Illustrious Chieftain of Junkyards divided his time between [[Metrobig City]] on [[Skor II]] and the [[Momship]] of the [[Squib Reclamation Fleet]]. The post of King of the [[Squib Polyanarchy]] may have been another name for the Illustrious Chieftain of Junkyards or an overlapping position.

